      "content": "q(x|y) = \\frac{p(x)}{Z(y)}e^{f(x,y)}",
      "start": 16289,
      "end": 16327
    },
    {
      "type": "latex_inline",
      "content": "(3)\n\nHere, q(x|y) is considered as an energy function in system [13],",
      "start": 16327,
      "end": 16401
    },
    {
      "type": "latex_inline",
